    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 60 students from the Media Informatics and Interactive Entertainment program at Mittweida University developed their own game over the course of two semesters.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Free the world from the capitalist robots</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the glamorous world of the 1920s and step into the role of the Goddess of Swing! In *Goddess of Swing*, you travel through dazzling, jazzy scenes while swinging through the air with your grappling hook and defeating enemies in fast-paced battles.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Feel the Swing</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the power of swing to mark your enemies with the Swing Zone and convert them back to Electro Swing through stylish moves. Every opponent becomes part of your rhythmic dance as you prepare for the grand showdown with epic bosses.</p>",
